Class AttendeeProfileFragment

java.lang.Object
androidx.fragment.app.Fragment
com.example.noram.AttendeeProfileFragment
All Implemented Interfaces:
android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, androidx.activity.result.ActivityResultCaller, androidx.lifecycle.HasDefaultViewModelProviderFactory, androidx.lifecycle.LifecycleOwner, androidx.lifecycle.ViewModelStoreOwner, androidx.savedstate.SavedStateRegistryOwner
public class AttendeeProfileFragment extends androidx.fragment.app.Fragment
A Fragment subclass. AttendeeProfileFragment is a fragment that displays the attendee's profile information It allows the user to edit their information and save it to the database. It also displays information about their profile stored in the database.
